description:
RealSimpleEDU.com brings you on-the-go learning and reference for Dental

App offers quizzes and tutorials  to help you learn Dental

App is continuously updated based on your feedback.Your 100% satisfaction is guaranteed.

App Tools include search .



Includes following tutorials:

Introduction to Dentistry,
Teeth Anatomy,
Adult Teeth Types,
Child Teeth Types,
Tooth Structure and Directions,
Tooth Development,
Wisdom Teeth,
Tooth Diseases (Gum),
Tooth Diseases (Cavities),
Dental Disease Prevention,
Dental Extraction,
Dental Implants,
Types of Implants,
Dental Braces,
Tooth Numbering System,
Radiography,
Dental Amalgam.


Includes following quizzes:

Quiz on Teeth Anatomy,
Quiz on Types of Teeth,
Quiz on Miscellaneous topic.


Our Vision: Provide on-the-go references that enable our customers to refer, learn and remember; easy to learn, more engaging and most complete.

Our Mission: A RealSimpleEDU app in every pocket.

Please write to us. We would love to improve this app.
